<p class="para1">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="para1">
  The results give us some intuitions about how to motivate users in a more effective way. On the present basis, not many people get motivated by outside forces, thus they often fail to accomplish their every day goals. Our app could focus more on these criteria.
</p>
